    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329430/extras/0ea9912510f2751361501590c401a116.avif?t=1749021253\" width=616 height=72 /></span>冒险者们不断涌向繁忙的小镇，探索新的地下城。作为初出茅庐的冒险者，你遇到了神秘而美丽的精灵玛蒂尔达。各自需要同伴的你们成为搭档，开始旅行。而在这段旅途中，你发现玛蒂尔达的能力与&quot;人际互动&quot;有着不一般的关联——你需要在危险的地下城中妥善处理这段复杂的关系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329430/extras/3d56ebd7f90da273da8377ff527a7172.avif?t=1749021253\" width=616 height=73 /></span>在共计30层的地下城中，展开为期30天的探索。地下城的每一层都会出现随机事件和挑战，通过探索和互动增强玛蒂尔达的能力，妥善处理你和玛蒂尔达的关系，将团队效率提到最大！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329430/extras/51e39c11216eb3795fda0a09a1a1d642.avif?t=1749021253\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329430/extras/bee4f0bc613fdb9cf45c715f0f4c8223.avif?t=1749021253\" width=616 height=350 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329430/extras/aee0fb1ceef7f4da45cb622334eb61df.avif?t=1749021253\" width=616 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329430/extras/ef4ce0742aa83b4c1b64c890b56cc4c7.avif?t=1749021253\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索动态的地下城</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满随机事件的肉鸽风格设计，足以提供紧张感与新鲜感。升级你的角色和装备，以备不时之需，深思熟虑地探索这个地下城！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超40张精美CG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发掘沉睡在地下城深处的秘密，加深你们的牵绊，沿途享受超过40张的精美CG！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能力提升系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过你与玛蒂尔达的关系提升她，发掘并了解她的个性与能力！</p>",
